==Esperanto==
===Etymology===
Esperanto interrogative/relative [[:Category:Esperanto correlatives|correlative]] prefix ''[[ki-]]'' + correlative suffix of objects ''[[-o]]''

===Correlative===
'''kio''' (''plural'' '''[[kioj]]''', ''accusative singular'' '''[[kion]]''', ''accusative plural'' '''[[kiojn]]''')

# [[what]] (the interrogative and relative correlative of objects)
#: Like other interrogative and relative correlatives, '''kio''' can be combined with ''[[ajn]]'', the adverbial particle of generality. '''''Kio''' ajn'' thus means ''[[whatever]]''.

